n=int(input('enter number:'))
oddsum=0
evensum=0
for i in range(1,n+1):
    if i%2==0:
        evensum=evensum+i
    else:
        oddsum=oddsum+i
print('sum of the even numbers:',evensum)
print('sum of the odd numbers:',oddsum)

Output:-------------

enter number:4
sum of the even numbers:6
sum of the odd numbers:4
